# .agent/ — Multi-Tool Agent Config Standard

Direktori ini menyimpan konfigurasi dan knowledge base yang digunakan **semua** AI agent tools
(Claude, Cursor, Kiro, Copilot, dll). Source of truth utama ada di root `../AGENTS.md`.

## Struktur

```
.agent/
├── README.md                    ← File ini
├── context/
│   ├── environment.json         ← Tech stack versions (multi-profile: windows/linux)
│   ├── project-context.json     ← Workspace routing, subprojects list
│   └── session-init.md          ← 6-step initialization protocol
├── memory/
│   ├── index.json               ← Memory index (entries + 10 categories)
│   └── entries/                 ← Knowledge entries per category
│       ├── config/
│       ├── context/
│       ├── decisions/
│       ├── errors/
│       ├── gotchas/
│       ├── implementation/
│       ├── learnings/
│       ├── optimization/
│       ├── patterns/
│       └── test/
├── skills/                      ← Modular agent capabilities (task-specific)
└── workflows/                   ← Operational workflows (.md files)
```

## Cara Pakai

- **Inisialisasi sesi** → baca `context/session-init.md` terlebih dahulu
- **Tambah lesson learned** → buat file di `memory/entries/<category>/<date>-<topic>.md`
- **Update memory index** → edit `memory/index.json`, update `last_updated`
- **Update AGENTS.md stats** → jalankan `/memory-promote` atau update manual

